Module me.sbasalaev.tybyco
Package me.sbasalaev.tybyco.descriptors

Class Jvm

java.lang.Object
me.sbasalaev.tybyco.descriptors.Jvm
public final class Jvm extends Object
Static methods and constants to build descriptors. When statically imported this class provides a cleaner way to make types and method descriptors. For instance, the descriptor for the Object.equals method is 
METHOD(BOOLEAN, TYPE(Object.class))
and the descriptor for List<? extends Number> type is 
TYPE(List.class, EXTENDS(TYPE(Number.class)))
